Module Game
Package Levels

Class Level

java.lang.Object
Levels.Level
Direct Known Subclasses:
LevelFromTxt, LevelOne, LevelTest
public abstract class Level extends Object
Template for generating mazes Includes one MainCharacter, two EventTiles and lists for walls, enemies and rewards Outermost ring consists of walls and beginning/end tiles
